installationInstructions.author: Marjon from Norristown, PA
installationInstructions.title: Vertical Mullion Rail was broken and detached partly from door
installationInstructions.content: Removed the middle screw and the whole rail came of. Unplugged wires and removed old rail. Plugged in the new rail and slid top and bottom slides on and put on the middle screw. Job finished
